topic.title: Upload on YouTube anonymously
topic.body: Is there really a way to upload a video anonymously on YouTube? Just the fact that to make a email address requests a valid telephone number is a limit, I tried with temporary phone numbers but nothing (maybe I was unlucky?). Do you have any suggestion?

1576109125_1AdBxG5bzX9cwPgGCJBvkSAL3dWkj.body: No, I mean the Google's YouTube.
